1. Clone it from git

```bash
https://github.com/BYVoid/OpenCC.git
cd OpenCC
```

2. Build sources.

```bash
cd src
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release -D ENABLE_GETTEXT:BOOL=ON ..
make
```

3. Install.

```bash
sudo make install
```

4.

ropencc is a project for conversion between Traditional and Simplified Chinese, wrapper in ruby.

Read the [wiki](http://code.google.com/p/opencc/wiki/Install) for more details.